init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is now in the process of trying to figure out what to do with him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is a story about an alien and a human who are friends, and who are trying to figure out how to make it work.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He will be able to explain to his people that he is not a kidnapper, but a writer.
